{"id":684,"parent_id":680,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":684,"title":"Ecclesiastes 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Eccl.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Oppression and evil deeds are vanity—The strength of two is better than one—Better is a poor and wise child than an old and foolish king."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.1","order":"02.22.004.44300"},["b","1"],"So I returned, and considered all the oppressions that are done under the sun: and behold the tears of",["i","such as were"],"oppressed, and they had no comforter; and on the side of their oppressors",["i","there was"],"power; but they had no comforter."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.2","order":"02.22.004.44301"},["b","2"],"Wherefore I praised the dead which are already dead more than the living which are yet alive."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.3","order":"02.22.004.44302"},["b","3"],"Yea, better",["i","is he"],"than both they, which hath not yet been, who hath not seen the evil work that is done under the sun."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.4","order":"02.22.004.44303"},["b","4"],"¶Again, I considered all travail, and every right work, that for this a man is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"envied"],"of his neighbour. This",["i","is"],"also vanity and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"vexation"],"of spirit."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.5","order":"02.22.004.44304"},["b","5"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"fool"],"foldeth his hands together, and eateth his own flesh."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.6","order":"02.22.004.44305"},["b","6"],"Better",["i","is"],"an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"handful"],["i","with"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"quietness"],", than both the hands full",["i","with"],"travail and vexation of spirit."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.7","order":"02.22.004.44306"},["b","7"],"¶Then I returned, and I saw",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"vanity"],"under the sun."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.8","order":"02.22.004.44307"},["b","8"],"There is one",["i","alone,"],"and",["i","there is"],"not a second; yea, he hath neither child nor brother: yet",["i","is there"],"no end of all his labour; neither is his eye satisfied with riches; neither",["i","saith he,"],"For whom do I labour, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"bereave my soul"],"of good? This",["i","is"],"also vanity, yea, it",["i","is"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"sore travail"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.9","order":"02.22.004.44308"},["b","9"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Two"],["i","are"],"better than one; because they have a good",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"reward"],"for their labour."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.10","order":"02.22.004.44309"},["b","10"],"For if they fall, the one will lift up his fellow: but woe to him",["i","that is"],"alone when he falleth; for",["i","he hath"],"not another to help him up."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.11","order":"02.22.004.44310"},["b","11"],"Again, if two lie together, then they have heat: but how can one be warm",["i","alone?"]],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.12","order":"02.22.004.44311"},["b","12"],"And if one prevail against him, two shall withstand him; and a threefold cord is not quickly broken."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.13","order":"02.22.004.44312"},["b","13"],"¶Better",["i","is"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"poor"],"and a wise child than an old and foolish king, who will no more be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"admonished"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.14","order":"02.22.004.44313"},["b","14"],"For out of prison he cometh to reign; whereas also",["i","he that is"],"born in his kingdom becometh poor."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.15","order":"02.22.004.44314"},["b","15"],"I considered all the living which walk under the sun, with the second child that shall stand up in his stead."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.16","order":"02.22.004.44315"},["b","16"],["i","There is"],"no end of all the people,",["i","even"],"of all that have been before them: they also that come after shall not rejoice in him. Surely this also",["i","is"],"vanity and vexation of spirit."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.4a","order":"02.22.004.44316"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.14"},"Gen. 26:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.4b","order":"02.22.004.44318"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/1.14"},"Eccl. 1:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.5a","order":"02.22.004.44320"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.28"},"2 Ne. 9:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.6a","order":"02.22.004.44322"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/15.16"},"Prov. 15:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.6b","order":"02.22.004.44324"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/silence"},"TG Silence"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.7a","order":"02.22.004.44326"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vanity"},"TG Vanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.8a","order":"02.22.004.44328"},["b","8a"],["span.small","OR"],"deprive myself."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.8b","order":"02.22.004.44330"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/1.13"},"Eccl. 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.9a","order":"02.22.004.44332"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/3.24"},"Moses 3:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.9b","order":"02.22.004.44334"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reward"},"TG Reward"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.13a","order":"02.22.004.44336"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.3"},"3 Ne. 12:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/4.13b","order":"02.22.004.44338"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teachable"},"TG Teachable"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/warn"},"Warn"],"."]]}
